title: Woodworking cold press machine US-MY-50T
title_uz: Yog'ochga ishlov beruvchi sovuq press uskunasi US-MY-50T
short_description: This US-MY-50T model woodworking cold press machine consumes a total of 4 KW per hour and has a working plate area of 1250 x 2500 mm. In addition, this equipment is capable of working at a speed of 180 mm per minute. The total dimensions of the equipment are 2860 x 1300 x 2550 mm, and the weight is 2600 kg.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-MY-50T modeldagi yog'ochga ishlov beruvchi sovuq press uskunasi soatiga umumiy 4 KW quvvat sarflaydi, shuningdek, undagi ish plitasining maydoni 1250 x 2500 mmni tashkil etadi. Bundan tashqari, ushbu uskuna daqiqasiga 180 mm tezlikda ishlash imkoniyatiga ega. Uskunaning umumiy o'lchamlari 2860 x 1300 x 2550  mm, og'irligi esa 2600 kgni tashkil etadi.
short_description_ru: Этот деревообрабатывающий станок холодного прессования модели US-MY-50T потребляет в общей сложности 4 кВт в час и имеет площадь рабочей плиты 1250 x 2500 мм. Кроме того, это оборудование способно работать со скоростью 180 мм в минуту. Габаритные размеры оборудования составляют 2860 х 1300 х 2550 мм, а вес 2600 кг.
short_description_en: This US-MY-50T model woodworking cold press machine consumes a total of 4 KW per hour and has a working plate area of 1250 x 2500 mm. In addition, this equipment is capable of working at a speed of 180 mm per minute. The total dimensions of the equipment are 2860 x 1300 x 2550 mm, and the weight is 2600 kg.
long_description:
Woodworking cold press machine US-MY-50T.

Technical parameters of the equipment:

  • Model: US-MY-50T.
  • Voltage: 380 V or as your request.
  • Total power: 4 KW.
  • Max working pressure: 50T.
  • Stroke: 1000 mm / 1200 mm / 1500 mm.
  • Work plate area: 1250 x 2500 mm.
  • Work plate length: 2500 mm / 3000 mm.
  • Working speed: 180 mm / min.
  • Dimensions: 2860 x 1300 x 2550 mm.
  • Net weight: 2600 kg.
long_description_uz:
Yog'ochga ishlov beruvchi sovuq press uskunasi US-MY-50T.

Uskunaning texnik ko’rsatkichlari:

  • Model: US-MY-50T.

  • Ish plitasining maydoni: 1250 x 2500 mm.
  • Ish plitasining uzunligi: 2500 mm / 3000 mm.
  • Ish tezligi: 180 mm / min.
  • Oʻlchamlari: 2860 x 1300 x 2550 mm.
  • Og'irligi: 2600 kg.
